data.description: Assumable loan at 2.25% interest rate!  Discover the epitome of modern comfort in this meticulously updated 4 bed, 3 bath home in the coveted Mead School District. Entertain effortlessly in the spacious park-like backyard oasis, complete with unparalleled privacy, waterfall with pond and a sparkling pool, ideal for lazy afternoons or lively gatherings. Embrace leisurely strolls or golf cart rides along the neighborhood path to the popular Wandermere Golf Course, while Pine River Park on the Little Spokane River offers idyllic picnics and outdoor adventures. Easy access to shopping, amazing restaurants, and the convenience of the new North-South Freeway. VA Hospital is a mere 9 miles away, ensuring both work and play are within reach. Welcome home!
